  "title": "Senior PMO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare consolidated WBS by collating Markets, CASA C DATA WBS</li><li>Prepare material for governance and ad-hoc meetings</li><li>Facilitate governance and stakeholder meetings on behalf of PMOs</li><li>Prepare and circulate the Minutes of Meetings</li><li>Follow up and close the action items from meetings</li><li>Maintain risk registers on behalf of PMOs</li><li>Track the deliverable status and facilitate the sign off process with stakeholders</li><li>Facilitate in tracking the cost (against AFA C Masterplan) and timeline</li><li>Compile details to be presented in CCB and RDA</li><li>Remind both PMOs (Markets C Release) on key dates/milestones</li></ul><p></p>",
